dct_title_s: South East Asia : continental series / map data & cartography by XYZ Digital Map Company
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. General map showing international boundaries, two types of roads, railways, and two types of airport. Shows disputed international boundaries. Includes chart showing flags, population, time zones, and calling codes for Southeast Asian countries.
